text: József Fabinyi (31 March 1887 - 1949) was a Hungarian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Hungarian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Hungary Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cluj-Napoca
